## Features âœ¨  

### ğŸ”Š Real-Time Transcription  
- Accurately transcribe lecture audio in real-time.  

### ğŸ–¼ï¸ Visual Content Recognition  
- Convert lecture slides and diagrams into text and searchable notes.

### ğŸ§® Equation Magic  
- Render complex equations into LaTeX for clear and organized representation.

### ğŸ“‹ Summarization & Organization  
- Generate concise summaries and structured outlines automatically.

### ğŸ—‚ï¸ Smart Note Organization  
- Tag, highlight, and categorize notes for easy access.

### ğŸŒ Multi-Language Support  
