---

## Tech Stack âš™ï¸  
- **React.js**: Dynamic user interface.  
- **Tailwind CSS**: Sleek, responsive design.  
- **React Speech Recognition**: Real-time transcription.  
- **Tesseract.js & Simpletex API**: Convert images to text and LaTeX.  
- **Mermaid.js**: Generate diagrams and flowcharts.  
- **Google Gemini LLM**: Integrate audio and visual data for cohesive notes.  
- **Firebase**: Secure, cloud-based note storage.

